      <odd id="aspace_475b595bee0c653c3ce0b8220f3f7ced">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-G (YRG 5-G), Records documenting personnel services at Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_ca91cc2517672af395419436e705a2ba">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Labor-Management Relations office, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_a16c0cde75aea636ff2b485b6ece4f5a">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The collection is partially restricted.  See collection contents for details.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_0336605575b24a162e881c652c2a3c1a">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Labor-Management Relations, Yale University, Records (RU 977). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_c1f993d0b2da589e6a27db95a9d27d79">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_6e4af9bcd4dd9a7a4a897065e0d2892d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, memoranda, and news clippings documenting contract negotiations between Yale and Local 34, Local 35, and the police union; union organizing drives; and labor strikes.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
